Local AI Harness — Part documentation index
===========================================

This repository is organized into harness components that can be operated independently:

- `harness/` runtime layer
- `harness/adapters/` model transport layer
- `deployment/` containerized local execution and ops
- Root config and entrypoint files (`harness.yaml`, `docker-compose.nvidia.yaml`, env templates)

